<item>
            <title>[FELIX-319] Mail handlers are not recognized by activation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-319</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;mail and activation are built as separate bundles.&lt;br/&gt;
The configuration for the mail handlers is in the mail bundle, but has to&lt;br/&gt;
be accessed from the activation bundle! Therefore the activation bundle&lt;br/&gt;
needs access to the META-INF/* configuration files and to the sun.* implementations.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The best solution is to bundle the activation jar inside the mail bundle. The applied patch makes the required changes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
